data.description: Magnolia Green MODEL HOME designed for today's modern lifestyle! THE MASON is a stunning plan offering 4,000+/- SQFT of living space. The amazing interior features an open foyer, dining room, OFFICE, family room with BRICK FIREPLACE and ARCHWAY to the morning room overlooking the PATIO, all flowing into a GOURMET KITCHEN ready for your farm table! GRANITE, an ISLAND with seating, and a COFFEE NOOK/WALK-IN PANTRY; the kitchen boasts all GE PRO appliances! There's a 1ST-FLOOR BEDROOM, FULL BATH, and mud room DROP ZONE from the garage! 2nd floor has an EXQUISITE OWNERS' SUITE w/2 closets and WALK-IN 12'X12' DRESSING ROOM with GRANITE ISLAND, a luxury en suite with vanities, shower w/DUAL SHOWER HEADS, and a SOAKING TUB. There are 3 additional bedrooms with JACK & JILL BATHS, laundry room, and a large LOFT/RECREATION area for family gathering or MEDIA space. Exterior features: 2-CAR side-entry garage, CONCRETE DRIVE, accent lighting, front/rear IRRIGATION, FENCED rear yard with PRIVACY evergreens and a FIRE-PIT PATIO perfect for relaxing or entertaining! Convenient to AWARD-WINNING Winterpock Elementary, Tomahawk Creek Middle, and Cosby High School! Buy it now before someone else does!
